Package: dir2json
Type: Package
Title: Convert Directory to JSON
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Convert a directory structure into a JSON format. This package lets you recursively traverse a directory and convert its contents into a JSON object, making it easier to import codebase from file systems into LLMs.
Author: Sam Parmar
Maintainer: Sam Parmar <your-email@example.com>
